window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A man will sacrifice anything for his family.</b> </p> <p>Facing the wrath of a Transcendent, John is forced to make a choice: He can either help humanity or pay for the crimes he committed. Unaware of what this involves, he is suddenly thrown into a war that has raged for eons. </p> <p>But the battlefield is bleak. The stakes are high, and humanity is losing. Despite ancient cultivation methods, their steady progress in the fight against Beastmen has vanished. Without change, only a dark defeat remains in the horizon. Can John and his allies save them?</p> <p>Listen to this sixth issue of The Idle System to find out. We canâ€™t promise an absence of planetary-level destruction or untold levels of martial prowess. If morality doesn't chain you, we welcome you in this journey!</p>"; 
